  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Hot and cold buffet breakfast with live egg station</li>
<li>Complimentary daily afternoon tea and cake</li>
<li>Three-course evening meal with choice of each course, served in the 'Stuva Grill'</li>
<li>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included</li>
<li>Guests are able to dine in 'Caschölin' - the new cheese restaurant - one night free of charge instead of their usual half board. There is a set menu with starter, fondue or raclette and a dessert on offer</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Steffani benefits from an ideal central location in the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St Moritz</a>, just 350 yards from the funicular to the <em>Corviglia Ski Area</em>. Daniela and Francesca Märky are the fourth generation of hosts who lovingly run the Hotel that has been the pride of St. Moritz since 1869.</p>
<p>Guests can dine on several worldwide delicacies available in house. Including Chinese in Le Mandarin, grilled dishes and fish in the Stuva Grill or typical Swiss and Italian cuisine in the Lapin Bley restaurant, which is the oldest restaurant in St Moritz.</p>
<p>The hotel also boasts 3 bars, the dance club Vivai and a hair and beauty salon. In addition to a state of the art spa area with indoor pool, sauna, steam bath, relaxation area and massage room.</p>]]></description>
