  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Basic Double </strong>rooms are relatively small at around 15m² and have a bath. These rooms face the garden or quiet side and can be used for single occupancy on request.</p>
<p><strong>Standard </strong>rooms have King or twin beds and are around 22-25m². These rooms have a bath or shower and can be used for single occupancy on request.</p>
<p><strong>Superior </strong>rooms have King or twin beds and are around 30m². These rooms also have a bath or shower and can be used for single occupancy on request.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe </strong>rooms are stylish and are 25-30m². These rooms have a balcony with mountain views and are on request so please call us to book.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Family </strong>rooms are around 30m² and sleep up to four using a double sofa bed (3 adults or 2 adults and 2 children). These rooms have a bath or shower and balcony with mountain view and are on request.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>offer the most space at around 36m². These rooms can comfortably sleep four using the double sofa bed in the lounge area (3 adults or 2 adults and 2 children). They also have a balcony and mountain views and are on request.</p>
<p><strong>Single</strong> rooms are around 16m² and have a shower and balcony. These rooms are also on request so please call us to book.</p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
